ine-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">软文写作究竟该如何着手?这对于很多新手来说，是个很大的问题，尤其是当要求写的软文对软度有要求的时候，就是更摸不着北了。软，要多少软才算软呢?这个度应该如何把握呢?如果简单的从文章来看，那些说什么百分之九十或者百分之七十的软度的人，很显然是不专业的，事实上，严格意义上来说，软文并不存在什么软度多少的问题。我们很多时候所谓的软度的问题，其实不过是对软文写作外行的一种感性的认识罢了，在这里，我将给大家讲授一些关于软文最基本的东西，只要掌握了这最基本的东西，软文的写作根本不是问题，剩下的只是纯粹的文字处理功力而已。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">我们说软文软文，只是相对于纯粹的硬广告而言的，既然和广告相对，那么这里面其实已经揭示了软文的本质。所谓对软文的划分，并不是针对写作技巧或者所谓软度的划分，而是针对角度和方法的划分。事实上，各种软文，我们如果从写作角度出发的话，那么再来看待软文，就一目了然了，那么写作起来也就会驾轻就熟了。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">软文的写作，一般有三个角度，其功效和影响是相辅相成的，并不存在着哪一个角度的软文更有杀伤力。真正要做好市场的宣传推广，那么就必须合理的安排这三个角度的软文写作。接下来，我就软文写作的三个写作角度做出一番的说明。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">第一个角度，是站在产品的角度，这也应该是软文和硬广告的分界点。硬广告因为其时间和文字字数限制的问题，所以它的宣传着重点在于以一种略带夸张的描述性方式来激起目标人群的感性成份。软文，则不是如此，它的核心是以其严谨的逻辑说理的形式来征服目标人群的理性成份。也就是说，站在产品的角度，硬广告可以夸张的说我们产品怎么怎么好，但一篇很好的软文却绝对不能如此空洞的描述产品，它要阐明的是我们的产品为什么好?它好在哪里?依据是什么?市场说明是什么?有什么数据和事实支撑?这是第一个角度写软文的特征。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">第二个角度，则是站在消费者的角度来写的，这个角度的话，写作技巧上是有一定的要求的，因为这个角度更多的是倾向于个人对产品的感受体验，在文字处理上必须感性点，又不能有更多宣传的痕迹。这个角度不能像第一个角度那样，带有产品的更多详细的资料和市场说明，因为一个消费者，它对产品只管好和不好，或者对比其他的同类产品，但都是很直白的好或者不好，用过之后感受也是肯定或者否定，没有其他什么理性的深入的分析产品之类的。这就是软文写作的第二个角度。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">至于第三个角度，就是站在第三方，既和产品没有任何关联的第三方角度，比如媒体或者专家权威机构的角度。这个角度的软文写作是最具专业性的，写软文的人必须想象自己就是个和产品没关系的人，在写之前你必须收集很多详细的资料。在内容的描述方面，不能带任何的主观用词，一切结论的得出都必须有数据和事实来支撑。站在这个角度写的话，有个秘诀，你不能简单的就以你要宣传的产品切入，而是以整个这类产品的整个市场切入，然后在对整个市场的考察分析中逐渐的引入你要宣传的产品。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">上面的三个角度其实就是写软文的关键所在，至于外行来说的多软这个软的问题，更多的时候是角度问题，比如第一个角度以外行来看，是不太软的，第二个角度，是相对软点的，第三个角度则是最软的。我们写软文，首先要考虑的不是软度的问题，而是角度的问题，哪个阶段用哪个角度来写，又或者这个角度多大的需要那个角度的配合，这才是我们要考虑的问题。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.33em 0px 20px; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; widows: auto;\">最后还有一点，就是软文题目的问题，很多人认为一篇软文的成败很大程度上取决于一个有震撼力的题目，这其实是一种很错误的观念，这种观念是建立在整个市场的成功就取决于这篇软文了的懒散和投机的思想上。事实上，软文真要起到作用，是不同角度的系列软文的组合。当你整个有了思路的话，其实题目在很多时候自然就出来了，而且肯定会有震撼力的，这是我的经验之谈。</p>','images/1/2015/09/NkpS8mMEokS1pu5B4S4s7T4UkOZK5Q.jpg',0,'微信家园','',0,'',760,1441509389,'','a:4:{s:6:\"status\";i:0;s:5:\"limit\";i:0;s:5:\"share\";i:0;s:5:\"click\";i:0;}'),(12,1,0,0,0,0,1,0,'','如何使用户分享文章到朋友圈？','','人性是自私的，但自私并不只是一个贬义词，其实只是一种很正常的表达。既然人性是自私的，怎么样促使他们主动分享到朋友圈？用户喜欢分享哪些文章到朋友圈？','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"images/1/2015/09/MRkxZ4tegKRKOtF5b1RO5pxRbXoJR3.jpg\" src=\"../attachment/images/1/2015/09/MRkxZ4tegKRKOtF5b1RO5pxRbXoJR3.jpg\" alt=\"images/1/2015/09/MRkxZ4tegKRKOtF5b1RO5pxRbXoJR3.jpg\" />一、分享是人天生的欲望</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">比如易粉这个平台，我们的线下活动会分享很多干货，这些干货对很多自媒体朋友来说都具有很大的价值，我相信大家都会主动的分享到朋友圈或者是向周围的朋友介绍易粉，这种分享就属于自发的，所以分享是人天生的欲望。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">二、人性自私</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">人性是自私的，但自私并不只是一个贬义词，其实只是一种很正常的表达。既然人性是自私的，怎么样促使他们主动分享到朋友圈？用户喜欢分享哪些文章到朋友圈？有一个大概的比例在这里</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.anyv.net/batch.download.php?aid=65434\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: none; max-width: 680px;\" src=\"http://www.anyv.net/datafile/2015/08/1_201508272357451kS3V.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #4f81bd; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">我总结了以下几点：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">第一、你的内容要<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&ldquo;有趣&rdquo;</span>，比如说冷笑话，类似这样有趣的内容大家都喜欢分享。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">第二、是<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&ldquo;有料&rdquo;</span>，就是干货，你的内容可以让别人学到东西，实用性较强。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">第三、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&ldquo;标题决定打开率&rdquo;</span>，一个文章的标题决定他的打开行为，标题要多琢磨一下怎样吸引更多人打开。但要适可而止，有的标题特别吓人，打开之后内容平平，令人失望，第一次有效果，第二次、第三次呢？归根结底还是内容决定转发，多写一些干货，有趣的内容，让用户自愿去转发。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; widows: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">第四、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&ldquo;转发=认同+表达&rdquo;</span>，转发包含两方面，一个是认同，另一个是表达。表达有很多种，比如你写的文章代表一种观点（兴趣、价值观等等），你的观点可以让别人找到一种认同感。再比如涨粉的问题，是众多微信运营者共同关心的话题，通过在易粉发起涨粉任务，再转发到朋友圈让具有相同目的性的运营者看到并加入，而加入的人也会邀请更多相同需求的人加入，这也属于一种认同。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #595959;\">什么时候推送文章好？</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #595959;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">主要是三个时间点，分别<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">是早上（上班的时间）、中午（吃饭的时间）、晚上（18点-22点左右），这是朋友圈传播最厉害的时候</span>，大家选择这个时间发，效果会更好。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">当然，这些都不是绝对的，有些时候因为<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">热点或者是其它人为原因，不一定非要遵循这个规律</span>，毕竟有些内容还是讲究时效性的。另外，最合适自己公众号的发送时间还需要你自己分析一下。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #595959;\">哪些文章传播比较快？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #595959;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">契约有一篇<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&ldquo;拒绝脑残，高效查出哪些微信好友删除了你&rdquo;</span>的文章传播比较快，相信很多朋友都频繁收到过微信好友群发的消息，为了不受到骚扰很多人就把这篇文章分享给好友来看。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">第二篇传播比较快的文章就是&ldquo;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">你在朋友圈接力坚持贩卖儿童判死刑，那只是在帮助人赚钱</span>&rdquo;，你在朋友圈里转发这个内容，希望贩卖儿童的罪犯判死刑，殊不知我们的同情和愤怒被人利用了，仔细看一下那条内容，下面植入了珍爱网的广告，转发的同时却帮别人做了广告。这篇揭秘文章一经发出，得到了大多数人的赞同和转发，直接就给&ldquo;移动互联网&rdquo;增加了3千多的粉丝，还有很多的报纸记者、媒体记者去采访契约。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">这两篇文章大众读起来比较容易理解，虽然通过科技账号发布出来，只能在小众范围之内传播，但是效果非常好。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #4f81bd; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">为什么呢？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4f81bd; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">为什么呢？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4f81bd; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">为什么呢？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4f81bd; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">因为受众普通、紧贴热点。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: &#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: #595959; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word;\">同样在7月8号的时候，股票大跌一片绿，我们就当下热点结合易粉自身特性做了一张宣传图，这张图片一经发出，立马刷爆了朋友圈，大家可以参考一下，比较戏剧性的一幕就是，第二天股票竟然大涨。</span></p>\r\n</div>','images/1/2015/09/MRkxZ4tegKRKOtF5b1RO5pxRbXoJR3.jpg',0,'爱妮微','',0,'',651,1441509927,'','a:4:{s:6:\"status\";i:0;s:5:\"limit\";i:0;s:5:\"share\";i:0;s:5:\"click\";i:0;}'),(13,1,0,0,0,0,1,0,'','估值一亿美金的微信公众号，你造吗？','','一条微信公众号创办大概也就一年的时间左右，目前有600万的粉丝，不需要销售人员每天都有很多人找上门要做广告，因为口碑好。','<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"images/1/2015/09/PPPgl03bQqBBpmfVQSuQP9p0f0oz5s.jpg\" src=\"../attachment/images/1/2015/09/PPPgl03bQqBBpmfVQSuQP9p0f0oz5s.jpg\" alt=\"images/1/2015/09/PPPgl03bQqBBpmfVQSuQP9p0f0oz5s.jpg\" />相信很多朋友都在做公众号，大部分都是在做广点通或者偶尔接接单。很多草根做梦都想着自己能做过牛逼的公众号，每个月能赚到万元以上。最近很多朋友更在吐槽说公众号现在的分成在严重缩水，我一朋友的几个号平时每个月能有60万左右收入的广告分成，最近突然缩水到只有10万了，再缩下去工资都发不起了。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">看来如果想赚到更多的钱单靠广点通分成估计是非常难的了，想想办法做点口碑做点特色接一些土豪广告主才是王道。很多做公众号的估计都知道有一个公众号特别牛逼，怎么样牛逼呢？每天只发一条内容，每一条内容都是视频，每一条视频都是广告，每一条广告收100万，每一条都是原创，每天都要无数广告订单，看到这里估计大家都知道它是谁了，没错它的名字就叫&ldquo;一条&rdquo;。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">一条微信公众号创办大概也就一年的时间左右，目前有600万的粉丝，不需要销售人员每天都有很多人找上门要做广告，因为口碑好。我是去年年尾的时候开始关注这个号的，是我一位做微信公众号很棒的朋友推荐我关注的。他做微信公众号目前也有几十万的粉丝。当初他给我介绍的时候说：财神哥你关注下这个公众号看看，最近推得很火。每天投广点通烧钱烧得很厉害，并且内容都是原创的很有意思。不过一条在当时做广点通的时候并不贵，听说只要几毛钱一个点击就可以了，现在要是做广点通吸粉估计没有3块以上一个粉是做不到了。广点通广告主的价格越来越贵了，而流量主的分成却越来越低了，因为移动端的广告资源比较少。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">一条刚刚创办的时候只有6个人，从0到100万的粉丝只用了短短的半个月时间，除了投广点通还从视频网站以及一些转发等迅速做到100万的粉丝。有一些名人也转发过他们的视频，如黄晓明、闾丘露薇等。一条的创始人徐沪生在访问时说道他的粉丝成本可能只用了别人的6分之1的成本，这样看来他的大部分粉丝应该不是在广点通中吸收的。更多的应该是在内容和转发中吸收的。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">如今一条已经完成了几轮融资，融资的金额达千万美金。而融资后一条的估计也达到了1亿美金，一个600万粉丝的微信公众号估计一亿美金这是什么概念？很多人可能不会相信。但是从营收来看你似乎会觉得合理一些，每月约3000万的收入。一条的核心价值观是要更多是做作品，似乎要推动中国生活美学的升级，而不是我们聚焦于营销，或者变现。其实说什么都是假，一条其实还是一个广告主。只是使用一种新的广告形式去变现，这个也是一条的价值所在。之所以有怎么多的广告主找上门其实就是因为口碑，100万一个广告并不是很多人能消费起。并且大部分的广告主都是一些实体的商家，比如一些做茶庄，做工艺，做品牌的商家。至于效果如何我们也不清楚，但是做这种广告更多的都是宣传品牌，因为商家都是全国各地的，实在真正能通过视频广告吸收到店的人估计不会很多。那么为什么收费怎么贵还怎么多的商家会找一条去推广呢？原因我认为除了一条的视频做得好，口碑好之外更多的是因为移动端的广告资源少。加上徐沪生以前一直在做传媒，传统的杂志也做过、所以在广告客户上面会有一定的累积。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">据统计2014年，电视媒体整体广告投放达到1.32万亿（刊例价），就算打个5折，也有差不多6000多亿。原则上，这些份额将来都属于互联网、移动互联网，市场巨大，但是却几乎没有一个高端一点的渠道，更不要说能够打通高端媒体与高端消费的平台了，这方面，视频将会是最强势的媒体形式。所以一条就是看中这个市场，结合人气最好用户最多微信做传播渠道。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">说真的刚刚开始就拿几百万去砸一个公众号不是谁都有这胆量的，更有胆量的是一轮轮的融资者，并且微信公众号将来会怎样谁也不知道。徐沪生说道他们早就开发好有自己的APP了，但是一直没有上，不想上。并且他们的社群为0，不做社群，就做内容。很多我们无法理解的运营方式，在一条上面我们看到了。拥有几百万的粉丝却不做社群，拥有几百万的粉丝和极好的口碑却不做自己的平台。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">目前消费一条内容的群体大部分都是草根，因为只有草根才有时间去消费内容。按照一条的内容来判断应该女性群体会比较多一点，但是一条并没有做电商的打算。视乎更多的想去做优质的内容，其实按照目前一条的粉丝群体和口碑做电商平台是最合适的，也是最容易获利和做大的方向。似乎我们都看不懂一条的下一步，徐沪生说道如果被你们看懂了一条的下一步他们是很危险的。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 40px;\">其实一条的成功就是因为专注，极致，快。所以各位创业者，不要想太多，看好市场，把控好方向把一个东西做到极致，做出价值你才能脱颖而出。还有一点就是要快，看准了就赶快做，在别人还没有看透你之前做起来。想法太多太聪明有时候并不是一件好事，我们很多的创业者，包括我自己也是因为想法太多。所以会分散很的精力去做一些无谓的事情，到头来发现我们连自己最初的想法都不见了。所以我目前也砍了很多项目，后期会专心做互传电商网和互传电商报APP，以提供优质内容为核心，没有太多的功能就做内容，把内容做到极致就好。其他的项目让其他人负责就好了，管太多，做太多我也发现真的会很难做大，这上半年发现自己还在原点。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: STHeiti; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 40px; widows: auto; background-color: #f4f4f4;\">微信公众号目前价值还是挺大的，虽然吸粉越来越难，特别是靠内容吸粉这块，但是如果你能把一直形式做到极致的话还是有机会的。别人的成功可以借鉴，但是不要模仿，因为往往做得好的人都是使用另一种我们还没有看清的思维去迅速做大的。同时还需要注意口碑，口碑这东西能给你带来无限的价值，也能减少你很多很多的<span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">推广成本。</span></span></div>','images/1/2015/09/PPPgl03bQqBBpmfVQSuQP9p0f0oz5s.jpg',0,'爱妮微','',0,'',978,1441510351,'','a:4:{s:6:\"status\";i:0;s:5:\"limit\";i:0;s:5:\"share\";i:0;s:5:\"click\";i:0;}'),(14,1,0,0,0,0,1,0,'','微信公众号推广之迅速加粉','','微信生意通现在已经是所有品牌和自媒体公认的最好推广渠道。坐拥6亿用户的平台，我们怎么可以运营一个公众账号并且可以在上面分一杯羹呢，让小编来讲解一下微信公众平台都有哪些推广方式吧。干货满满希望对你有帮助','<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">　<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"images/1/2015/09/AsIoq8nbLN0s0aBAhS8h0qZs3NWAib.jpg\" src=\"../attachment/images/1/2015/09/AsIoq8nbLN0s0aBAhS8h0qZs3NWAib.jpg\" alt=\"images/1/2015/09/AsIoq8nbLN0s0aBAhS8h0qZs3NWAib.jpg\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">一.微信公众号推广</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　一段精彩的&ldquo;废话&rdquo;之后，告诉你如何做新媒体推广&mdash;&mdash;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　进入正题之前，先分享一点个人感受。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　1、不要盲目崇拜而迷失了自己的方向</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　几乎每天都能听到或者看到很多大号的分享，讲如何重视内容，如何差异化，如何坚持等等，&ldquo;听了这么多道理，依旧过不好这一生&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　大言不惭的讲，除开少数的大神之外，普遍的大号都有着三个特点或之一：一、把握红利期(做的早);二、原本在互联网上就有所积累(比如论坛红人、博客达人、出过书等);三、公司化运作(一个公司运作几十个大号)。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　PS：当然，并不是否定这些大号的成功之处，只是建议尤其是新人朋友，不要盲目崇拜而迷失了自己的方向。再小的个体也是品牌，个体!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　2</span>、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">不谈内容和定位</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　太多的人在讲这两点的重要性了(当然，我也写过)。这次略过~</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　3、别再做着日增过万的美梦</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　请不要再每天想着突然有一天，粉丝增长一天过万甚至好几万。我信因果，任何爆发式的增长都是有原因的，哪怕是你碰巧，背后一定有其可以研究和学习的原因。而研究这个原因的过程就是学习进步的过程。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　所以，踏踏实实，一步一个脚印，个人建议。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">　　</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">二.微信公众平台推广干货</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　废话了这么多，担心各位看官等急了，先放个大招，推广三步走：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　1、你的用户是谁：根据产品和业务分析用户画像，了解用户的需求和痛点。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　2、用户在哪里：具备上述画像条件的用户出现和聚集在什么地方，贴吧还是网吧。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　3、如何吸引过来：知道用户的需求了，也知道在什么地方了，那就思考用什么方法能引起他们的兴趣，吸引他们注意，并且成功转化。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">　　</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">三.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">微信公众平台推广方式</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　所有的推广方法都分为两种：花钱的和不花钱的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　最伟大的真理诞生了：花钱省时间，花时间省钱。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　(注意，说这句正确的废话并不是我调戏大家，而现实是很多运营者包括决策者总是会纠结这两个问题，到底是花钱，还是花时间，最后钱也花了，时间也花了。成本上涨，红利已过，效率极低，然后还一脸鄙夷的说，新媒体果然没什么用。)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　下面的方法，哪个花钱可以省时间，哪个可以花时间省点钱，自行判断。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　1、网站广告推广微信公众号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; widows: auto; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 23px;\">　　广点通、QQ群广告、网络推广(</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.anyv.net/\" target=\"_blank\">微信大全&nbsp;http://www.anyv.net/&nbsp;</a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 23px;\">)，通过广点通砸出一万两万的粉甚至更多，然后再利用自己的原创内容和服务维系粉丝，绝对值得一试。&ldquo;一条&rdquo;不就是这么干的么?据说三天砸出百万粉丝，从那以后，各大媒体免费报道，自己的图文条条10万+。(再好的内容需要有基础粉丝群体传播，所以快速获取基础粉丝，个人认为非常关键!)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　2、微信大号推广微信号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　也是广告的一种，不同的是这种推广方式更适合活动推广，找跟你的粉丝属性比较吻合的大号，比如本地号，美食号，科技号，女性号等等，微博和微信包括知乎、豆瓣都有这样的群体。(值得注意的是，现在很多公司和团队商业化运作之后，这种推广的水份也越来越大，建议大家如果有类似的需求可以找找身边的朋友，现在自媒体这么多，没准你身边的朋友的隔壁就住着一个坐拥数十万甚至百万粉丝的大号。)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　3、粉丝社群推广微信号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　社群这个词，估计还会火一段时间，并且现在谁的微信上没几个群聊呢?提到这个粉丝社群，先普及一个观点。文章的阅读数跟哪些因素有关?有标题、有配图、有内容、还有粉丝数量、还有转发等等。对，这里要说的就是转发。粉丝社群建立起来除了跟粉丝更好的进行互动之外，就是利用一些玩法能够让粉丝将内容转起来，哪怕你卖个萌，哪怕你发个红包。70%的内容都是从朋友圈阅读，这个道理，你不会不懂吧?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　4、活动策划</span>推广微信号</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　前段时间风靡的合体红包、助力加油这些应用，就是活动的一种，另外特别实用的比如&ldquo;投票&rdquo;、&ldquo;征名&rdquo;、&ldquo;抽奖&rdquo;&hellip;虽然官方禁止集赞，但是还是有些商家利用集赞做到比较好的效果。一个好的时机，一个好的奖品，一个好的玩法加上一个好的推广，是能够形成一个好的活动的，而结果就是，这就是一个好的推广。(当然了，动动嘴皮子是很简单的，做起来就会有很多细节要把握了，有需要的可以联系本人，定制活动策划500一份，童叟无欺。)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　5、利用微信公众账号互推</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　是不是以为&ldquo;买粉&rdquo;之后又是个骚点子，互推算是最经济实惠的方法了，放在&ldquo;买粉&rdquo;之后，当然是有道理的，你没有粉丝，谁愿意跟你互推呢?(会不会被打?)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　当然了，互推是在公平对等，诚信做人的基础之上进行的，以上行为强烈抵制!那么在互推的时候如何擦亮双眼分析对方的粉丝真实性以及粉丝属性的吻合程度，也是一门功课，甚至可能付出血的教训。还是那句话，总是有第一次的嘛~别太在意了</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　6、地面推广</span>微信公众号</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　在目前的非红利期，地推无疑是成本相对较低，最直接有效的方式了，最关键的是，很多高高在上的运营大咖们不屑于去做的事情，那么这就是差异化和机会!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; widows: auto; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 23px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">　　举个最简单的例子，一个苹果、一支笔就能换一个粉丝关注，甚至如果你颜值够高，够猛够萌，可能一个表情就搞定了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: #333333; fon